ion Contract, Katana, Ninja Robes and Mask, Tantō (Dagger), 1d10 Kunai</p>\n<h3><strong>II. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.jrHEBqdPezyDHMdn]{Chunin}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.sRuMlaPU5xdIrwhd]{Climb}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.AkjRsazdAppqveZu]{Pick Lock}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.UQgNIecnmaguYegE]{Ranged (Explosives)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.McTtmZu3Ac8Lh48W]{Stealth (Any)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Explosives)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.g4Q6AtzZuo5iIvD4]{Catfall}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.MGEPI4jNhymNIRVz]{Scale Sheer Surface}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.XSb3QVB9ipPBFt56]{Shadow}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.RWJrupj9seau0w31]{Strike to Injure}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bomb Crafting Recipes, Ninja Hideout, 10 Shuriken</p>\n<h3><strong>III. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.inI3ZxiOd8E2fGsA]{Jonin}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.ZqYYWZuWwqMb3wVf]{Melee (Flail)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.vQtJqX0qb0bbpVDg]{Perform (Acrobatics)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.ZQSm2AwrgT2cHG0C]{Ranged (Bow)}&nbsp;<em>or </em>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.KQjZ85kKz42YQGYT]{Ranged (Sling)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.McTtmZu3Ac8Lh48W]{Stealth (Any)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.GU1KpgY3MeFIaDaq]{Careful Strike}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.TaYriYcJkFuIdBKp]{Contortionist}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.E3vTSCzgrasNijUO]{Fleet Footed}, @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.talents-nom.Vx2IN7tFgRYOjv5v]{Martial Artist}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Chain and Sickle, High-end Assassination Contract, 3 Torinoko Grenades</p>\n<h3><strong>IV. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.yV9rwfZvsviWCzAZ]{Master Jonin}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.fdq3RFSOKl5b3WzW]{Art (Any)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.0LdHytqyNmg2pcAX]{Combat Aware}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.tXKX29QZBdHmyMc7]{Combat Reflexes}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.8pVzgPkgWpTJvfhG]{Fearless (Guards)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.Z91GFaT6FhEwyESU]{Tunnel Rat}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Business Front and HQ, Genin Apprentice, Quality Clothing</p>"}
{"name":"Man-At-Arms","permission":{"default":0,"lNumE4kwYfzQkIkY":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.597AUOs60vVJzpqj"}},"content":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Man-At-Arms</h1>\n<blockquote>&ldquo;Young Jean-Marie is out there with the other lads. He&rsquo;s been practicing standing straight all last year, we hope milord will pick him to be a man-at-arms!&rdquo;<br />\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&mdash;Eudes Bisset, L&rsquo;Anguillian Peasant</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&ldquo;Kid, I&rsquo;ve seen enough war for three lifetimes. It&rsquo;s all shit. Sure, we march and charge at the Duke&rsquo;s command, and we bow and scrape nice and good for him. But when the clash begins? Best hope The Lady is watching over you, for the Duke sure isn&rsquo;t.&rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">- Onfroi, Paravonnese Man-at-Arms</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Though noble knights are the most prominent and famous of the forces of Bretonnia, it is humble, lowborn Men-at- Arms who make up the bulk of Bretonnian armies. Whether they be simple peasant levies, given basic weapons and little training, or professional soldiers with sturdy equipment and ample pay, Men-at-Arms are ubiquitous in any Bretonnian fighting force.</p>\n<p>Experienced Men-at-Arms are just as capable as the noble knights, though rarely as well-equipped. Men-at-Arms know when to be noticed, when to fight hard, and when to run.</p>\n<p>Men-at-Arms can be seen all across Bretonnia and even beyond, defending their homes or campaigning in foreign lands for their lords.</p>\n<p>Between musters, Men-at-Arms often occupy themselves with garrison duty and other forms of service or return to non-military jobs. Many will accompany noble lords and knights on quests, or travel to perform tasks on behalf of their masters. Some turn to adventure, mercenary work, or banditry during these extended periods of leave.</p>\n<p><strong>Species:&nbsp;</strong>Human (Bretonnian Peasant)</p>\n<p><strong>Class:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Man-At-Arms Advance Scheme</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 634px; height: 32px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 69px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">WS</td>\n<td style=\"width: 60px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">BS</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">S</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">T</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Agi</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Dex</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Int</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">WP</td>\n<td style=\"width: 63px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Fel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 69px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 60px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">II</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">III</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 63px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">IV</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>I. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.BIB8Sbky850tGCqJ]{Peasant Levy}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @Compendium[w