@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Magic)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.Ywo6fZNPC4zbHHSQ]{Strong-minded}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Courtly Garb, Lamellar Coat</p>\n<h3><strong>IV. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.WRmX6JVTvDYTdwgd]{Celestial Prefect}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.pKLMbmG3Ivt6mzMf]{Haggle}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Politics)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.mqo51ORnxijcqNNu]{Frightening}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.eowbsW6oHGSNJmxV]{Magic Resistance}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.6w30u0VPsAicrqb5]{Magical Sense}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.wNvPXAhlKABl6hpk]{Pure Soul}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Large Spy Ring of Imperial Agents, Quality Courtly Garb</p>","_id":"UdPr6ld9ePEinK3j"}
{"_id":"XLZCmtgVu0qjhiUl","name":"Lustrian Luchador","permission":{"default":0,"lNumE4kwYfzQkIkY":3},"folder":"","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.qk9A050gAk5oWQ1V"}},"content":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lustrian Luchador</h1>\n<blockquote>&ldquo;By the honor of mi familia and in the name of Myrmidia, I challenge YOU El Toro Furioso to a championship match! Should you refuse, your cowardice shall stain your legacy for eternity! You, me and all of Magritta. We will see who is the real Campe&oacute;n del Magritta is.&rdquo;&rdquo;<br />\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&mdash;Raymundo El F&eacute;nix, Legendary Luchador from the New World</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The followers of the goddess of War herself are experts of trial by combat, with Estalians and Tileans to this day both claiming to be the true descendants of her lineage. Conflicts predictably arise, and nowhere is this more prevalent than through honorable duels and trials by combat in her name with mixed results. In Tilea, wrestling is a past-time that stretches back thousands of years of the people&rsquo;s history, with leaders like Lorenzo Lupo claiming to be unbeatable in the ring. Estalians are fans of the eccentric and fashionable who take pride as the birthplace of modern dueling and sporting the finest duelists in the Old World. Deep within the Estalian colony of Santa Magritta in the New World these two cultures mixed as floods of colonists from Tilea and Estalia made their way to the New World, and by the early 1900&rsquo;s the Lustrian Luchador was born.</p>\n<p>The luchadors are predominantly devout worshippers of Myrmidia and champions of honorable combat via wrestling and spectacle. Much like their pit fighter counterparts, luchadors enter into a ring against one or multiple opponents and must battle their way to victory; however, rules and guidelines ensure the general safety of the individuals in the ring, as the purpose isn&rsquo;t so much to spill blood as it is to overcome your opponent by pinning them to the ground using a combination of skill, strategy and brute strength. Luchador rings are square shaped and roped off, unlike the circular pits most seen in the Old World for pit fighters. As are the ways of Myrmidia martial weapons are not allowed in these matches, but loopholes have allowed the use of chairs, debris and other various non-lethal items thrown into the ring to be commonly used by luchadors in an attempt to gain an advantage in a fight.</p>\n<p>Luchadors and their wrestling culture has a strong mixture of performance art and aesthetic iconography, with many luchadors taking on unique themes based on different cultures or religions from across the world. Luchadors sport exotic masks that cover most of their facial features&mdash;these help them to play a character to help excite the crowd and allow the crowd to recognize the wearer. El Hombre Muertos for instance is a legendary Morrian luchador who dresses in black and purple, wears a mask with a skull pattern and cites scripture from the Libro Dei Morti to intimidate his opponents before a match.</p>\n<p>These themes modeled after the eccentric characteristics from the diestros of Estalia combined with the intense wrestling of the Tileans make for a unique and highly popular spectacle for the people of both cultures to enjoy. Its popularity has recently spread to the Old World, with Magritta and Miragliano now housing their own leagues of luchador wrestling, with other species such as Dwarfs, Halflings and even Ogres having begun to participate in the sport. Its popularity has allowed many luchadors to grow extremely wealthy in the process as they win matches and rise through the ranks to earn championship titles and become legends that will be remembered for centuries.</p>\n<p><strong>Species:&nbsp;</strong>Human, Dwarf, Halflinf</p>\n<p><strong>Class:&nbsp;</strong>Warrior</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lustrian Luchador Advance Scheme</h3>\n<table style=\"width: 634px; height: 32px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 69px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">WS</td>\n<td style=\"width: 60px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">BS</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">S</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">T</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Agi</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Dex</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Int</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">WP</td>\n<td style=\"width: 63px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Fel</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 69px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 60px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">I</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">II</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">III</td>\n<td style=\"width: 61px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 62px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 63px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">IV</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>I. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.LOz7KR7aMrIOA5t1]{Aprendiz}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @Compendium[wfrp4