LhyOYwcyMUl]{Flee!}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.q58lK4kULJZB5GjE]{Rover}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bedroll, Hand Weapon, Leather Jerkin, Tinderbox</p>\n<h3><strong>II. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.BwrxVe2Tg67eP0fx]{Highwayman}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.7pQo66cESWttzIlb]{Gamble}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.os4NKy5Oy6sRt1eh]{Outdoor Survival}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.oSbEE6eXH1S3LfUU]{Ride (Horse)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.Xk5tp3aasPNtk4zt]{Stealth (Rural)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.IFKWu98qmWpaSfUi]{Ambidextrous}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.edsenrEYTLOtpa6b]{Crack the Whip}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.5lcttqGToT54WFrl]{Marksman}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.9CAkY3SQjQxRTlNJ]{Roughrider}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Coat, Hat (Tricorn), Mask, Pistol with 10 Bullets, Riding Horse with Saddle and Tack, Tent</p>\n<h3><strong>III. @Compendium[nations-of-mankind-wfrp4e.careers-nom.fNGaSUcKo3NshSZY]{Gang Leader}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.iYan4z52v7HYM9u9]{Drive}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.OuDdJRDo3W56zk0Z]{Ranged (Crossbow)}&nbsp;<em>or </em>@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.UQgNIecnmaguYegE]{Ranged (Explosives)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Criminals)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.8pVzgPkgWpTJvfhG]{Fearless (Road Wardens)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.0ep8BNMiZGVLTHpr]{Gunner}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.0hn6UaKq8CoZP2zD]{Menacing}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Gang of Highwaymen, M